pageContext.claim: “I said, I haven't spoken to Russia in years. What the hell do I have to do with Russia?”
pageContext.analysis: Trump signed a letter of intent for Trump Tower Moscow in October 2015, and his former personal attorney, Michael Cohen, has testified that he was pursuing the project on Trump’s behalf in 2015 and 2016. The Mueller report says Trump declined to answer questions from the special counsel about the Moscow project.
